Package: mlr3batchmark
Title: Batch Experiments for 'mlr3'
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Michel",
           family = "Lang",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "michellang@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9754-0393"))
Description: Extends the 'mlr3' package with a connector to the
    package 'batchtools'. This allows to run large-scale benchmark
    experiments on scheduled high-performance computing clusters.
